title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - The Hague
description:
In this video we will look at a community addon which updates the municipality of the Hague with a lot of additional content. So if you love flying in the Netherlands using MSFS this is definitely something which you might want to give a try.

If you want to give the scenery a try visit the link below to download it
